        "text": "Linux 使用 Arch Linux WSL2 环境完成构建并发布压缩包。"
      }
    ],
    "en": [
      {
        "type": "feature",
        "text": "Added a Windows EXE installer packaged with Inno Setup."
      },
      {
        "type": "improvement",
        "text": "Windows release build now uses release, obfuscation, split-debug-info, and tree-shake-icons optimizations."
      },
      {
        "type": "improvement",
        "text": "Published Android release packages for armv7, arm64, and x86_64 ABIs."
      },
      {
        "type": "feature",
        "text": "Web is now built with WASM and pushed to Yaru-VerWeb for push-to-deploy publishing."
      },
      {
        "type": "improvement",
        "text": "Linux was built in an Arch Linux WSL2 environment and published as a compressed package."
      }
    ]
